text: Bishanchander Seth is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, the lower house of the Parliament of India as a member of the Hindu Mahasabha. ==References== ==External links== *Official biographical sketch in Parliament of India website Category:1909 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Lok Sabha members from Uttar Pradesh Category:2nd Lok Sabha members Category:3rd Lok Sabha members Category:Hindu Mahasabha politicians
